    <title>实验及latex测试</title>
    <url>/2023/11/04/%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E5%8F%8Alatex%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>测量其周期，以30个为一个单位进行测量，以减少计时所带来的误差</p>
<p>改变物块的位置，最后通过线性拟合计算出其转动惯量</p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>b</mi><mtext>为物体过质心转动惯量与杆的转动惯量，</mtext><mi>k</mi><mtext>为与位置有关的</mtext><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>l</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mtext>项</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">b为物体过质心转动惯量与杆的转动惯量，k为与位置有关的ml^2项
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8641079999999999em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">b</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">为</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">物</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">体</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">过</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">质</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">心</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">转</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">动</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">惯</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">量</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">与</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">杆</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">的</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">转</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">动</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">惯</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">量</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">，</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">k</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">为</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">与</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">位</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">置</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">有</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">关</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">的</span><span class="mord mathdefault">m</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.01968em;">l</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8641079999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">项</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>问题</p>
<p>在实验过程中发现其振幅会因阻力较为快速的衰减，对实验结果有不小的影响，进行修正</p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mtext>首先，设其受一与角速度成线性关系的力矩：</mtext><msub><mi>M</mi><mi>f</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>A</mi><mover accent="true"><mi>θ</mi><mo>˙</mo></mover><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mtext>则其运动方程变为：</mtext><mi>I</mi><mover accent="true"><mi>θ</mi><mo>¨</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mi>A</mi><mover accent="true"><mi>θ</mi><mo>˙</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mi>l</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mtext>初始条件为：</mtext><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>θ</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mtext>，</mtext><msub><mover accent="true"><mi>θ</mi><mo>˙</mo></mover><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>θ</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mi>A</mi><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>I</mi></mrow></mfrac><mi>t</mi></mrow></msup><mrow><mo fence="true">[</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mi>t</mi><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>A</mi><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>I</mi><mi>ω</mi></mrow></mfrac><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mi>ω</mi><mi>t</mi><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow><mo fence="true">]</mo></mrow><mtext>，</mtext><mi>ω</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mi>l</mi></mrow><mi>I</mi></mfrac><mo>−</mo><msup><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mfrac><mi>A</mi><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>I</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mtext>数据处理这一点暂时待定，通过改变</mtext><mi>l</mi><mtext>而进行拟合似乎不是很方便？</mtext><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mtext>当然也还好，比如衰减项？</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">首先，设其受一与角速度成线性关系的力矩：M_f=-A\dot{\theta}
\\
则其运动方程变为：I\ddot{\theta}+A\dot{\theta}+mgl{\theta}=0
\\
初始条件为：{\theta}(0)={\theta _0}，\dot{\theta} _0=0
\\
\theta =\theta _0e^{-\frac{A}{2I}t}\left[ \cos \left( \omega t \right) +\frac{A}{2I\omega}\sin \left( \omega t \right) \right]，\omega =\sqrt{\frac{mgl}{I}-\left( \frac{A}{2I} \right) ^2}
\\
数据处理这一点暂时待定，通过改变l而进行拟合似乎不是很方便？
\\
当然也还好，比如衰减项？
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.969438em;vertical-align:-0.286108em;"></span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">首</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">先</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">，</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">设</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">其</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">受</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">一</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">与</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">角</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">速</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">度</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">成</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">线</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">性</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">关</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">系</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">的</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">力</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">矩</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">：</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">M</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3361079999999999em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.10903em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.286108em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.01463em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mord acce